OL,5,G0610 Martin Clunes: Islands of
OL,6,G     Australia
OL,7,     FThe actor explores Mundoo Island,
OL,8,     Fwhich has provided a way of life
OL,9,     Ffor five generations of one
OL,10,     Ffarming family, and also
OL,11,     Finvestigates Phillip Island.
OL,12,G0710 Man and Beast with Martin Clunes
OL,13,     FComedy actor Martin Clunes travels
OL,14,     Fto Nepal, where he meets a farmer
OL,15,     Fwhose cows not only provide milk,
OL,16,     Fbut also the fuel for lighting and
OL,17,     Fcooking in his home.
