OL,5,G2000 Bangers & Cash
OL,6,     FAston DB4/Tractor: Derek heads off
OL,7,     Fto Colchester to pick up a 1960
OL,8,     FAston Martin DB4 that has been
OL,9,     Fsitting under a tarpaulin in a
OL,10,     Fgarage that has collapsed round it
OL,11,     Ffor 40 years.
OL,12,G2100 Bangers & Cash
OL,13,     FHonda NSX/Range Rover: Dave is
OL,14,     F'lost in France' en route to
OL,15,     Fpicking up a rare Honda NSX. Derek
OL,16,     Fheads to a toy factory where some
OL,17,     Fvintage motorbikes are stashed.
